title: La Chatia Artesana
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Pizza, Fast food, Take-out, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Formerly called Artesano Panaderia and Bakery. Bakery cafe with Wi-Fi. Makes breads, bagels, pizza, and sandwiches with tofu, tempeh, and vegetable. Vegans ask to omit cheese in sandwich. Beverages include juice and coffee. Has stuffed breads for take out. Occasionally has vegan cakes.
